        />

        <!--
                    BF at the start of the color means 75% transparancy
                    Hex opacity values:
    100% — FF
    95% — F2
    90% — E6
    85% — D9
    80% — CC
    75% — BF
    70% — B3
    65% — A6
    60% — 99
